"hypervisor. It has some additional features over the raw format, such "
"as:<placeholder-1/>"
msgstr " <link href=\"http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/QEMU/Images\">qcow2</link> （QEMU 写时复制版本2）格式通常是KVM使用，相比裸格式，它有额外的特性，例如：<placeholder-1/>"

