msgstr "Rackspace 云运行商维护了多个发行版（Red Hat, CentOS, Fedora, Ubuntu）预先创建的镜像列表。列表的链接为<link href=\"https://github.com/rackerjoe/oz-image-build\">rackerjoe/oz-image-build on GitHub</link>。"

#: ./doc/image-guide/ch_obtaining_images.xml140(title)
